###

# Audit trail — validate publish→complete lifecycle for orders-queue
# Run after the batch publish (and after the worker has consumed the messages)
# Each entry shows:
#   Publish.Status:  Queued → Published  (set by SamplePublisher.Api)
#   Receive.Status:  Received → Processing → Completed  (set by SampleWorker.Queue)
GET {{host}}/audit/trail?destination=orders-queue&since=30
Accept: application/json

###
